title: 17 - Wil Sylvince
itunes:title: 17 - Wil Sylvince
description: We managed to catch Wil Sylvince in Las Vegas just before he left to open for Dave Chapelle, so you know this one’ll be good. You’ve seen him on Comedy Central, Def Comedy Jam, and Showtime, now hear his story, plus another bonus story about the legendary Patrice O’Neal. Here’s five words to describe this episode: it’s totally worth about $1000.
